as a developer

   type npm install in order to start setup for node.
   run node server.js in the terminal.
   Send a POST request in another tab with: http POST :3000 name=
   Send a GET request with: http GET :3000/api/user/
   Send a PUT request with: http PUT :3000/api/user/ name=<name
   run the mocha in terminal to see if it passes the test








      
